{"tid":1544903,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"98係美領合唱美國國歌同《願榮光歸香港》","createTime":"2019-09-05T17:10:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T15:02:13.000Z","uid":129622,"like":67,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"56d6bb623330a7aef6f83e5fe769687a87bea191","tid":1544903,"uid":129622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:10:15.000Z","msg":"要認真比國際聽一次我地把聲<br />\n同時做個紀錄<br />\n要令呢首歌成為習慣<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fy7yRDOLCy4Y&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWD2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=d332d533\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y</a><br />\n<br />\n何以這土地淚再流？<br />\n何以令眾人亦憤恨？<br />\n昂首拒默沉，吶喊聲響透，<br />\n盼自由歸於這裏！<br />\n何以這恐懼抹不走？<br />\n何以為信念從沒退後？<br />\n何解血在流，但邁進聲響透？<br />\n建自由光輝香港！<br />\n在晚星墜落徬徨午夜，<br />\n迷霧裏最遠處吹來號角聲，<br />\n捍自由，來齊集這裏，來全力抗對，<br />\n勇氣、智慧，也永不滅。<br />\n黎明來到，要光復這香港，<br />\n同行兒女，為正義時代革命（獲勝利）。<br />\n祈求民主與自由萬世都不朽，<br />\n我願榮光歸香港！"},{"pid":"75a0a0b2567ec2eeb1ce6edf6e20a78efe60a33f","tid":1544903,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:10:25.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9351013130050e1fe98fa2935025d330fcf2a518","tid":1544903,"uid":117906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:11:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"61dc362be02ddf2423f5f35b2726c02c00c9f41b","tid":1544903,"uid":290468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:11:55.000Z","msg":"支持，文宣手足多d宣傳首歌"},{"pid":"78e89012107fd646605db0759ea28b29d1cdaa8e","tid":1544903,"uid":268725,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:12:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8B39Niu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8B39Niu.png&h=c9eeccd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5722c7a62d9c3c2d27e440a243b220e2d7aa44e8","tid":1544903,"uid":168522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:13:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推呀"},{"pid":"c020ce20916feb08f6728e3739b8f03895270452","tid":1544903,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:15:57.000Z","msg":"好好聽"},{"pid":"21e1f2688e779e34f1ebce97a2d3dbab63a83ad9","tid":1544903,"uid":282494,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:21:14.000Z","msg":"收手啦漢奸